OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThere will
OL,6,Fbe a mixture of clear intervals and
OL,7,Fshowers, these more frequent over
OL,8,FMoray in the evening and early night.
OL,9,FLight and variable winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA few bright or sunny spells
OL,12,Fotherwise rather cloudy. Mainly dry
OL,13,Fwith just a few scattered showers.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,16,Fon Saturday with the chance of a few
OL,17,Fshowers. Dry start Sunday then rain
OL,18,Fspreading from northwest, lasting into
OL,19,FMonday before it brightens up later.
